HEADWORD: Clavichord
<hw>Clav"i*chord</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>clavicorde</ets>, fr. L. <ets>clavis</ets> key + <ets>chorda</ets>
